sub_title: Graduate of the University of Amsterdam
summary:
I am a recent graduate of the University of Amsterdam. Throughout my entire life, I have been immersed in the international atmosphere of my school and later the multicultural dynamics of my higher education. It allowed me to develop as a flexible, sensitive, and brave person. I am not afraid to face challenges and learn new skills in the process. 
Currently, I am good at brainstorming original ideas and marketing solutions and creating social media content. In addition, as a communication science professional, I know how to execute social experiments and questionnaires to check communication-related hypotheses. Thus, my activities in the marketing field are mostly based on data and scientific research as well as experimenting and a "try-fail" approach.
